rows.label: tlk001201_06_msg0001
rows.name:
It seems you have obtained
the third sword and recovered
the Heaven's Holy Grail.

rows.label: tlk001201_06_msg0002
rows.name:
And now, you head for the
World Tree, I take it.

rows.label: tlk001201_06_msg0003
rows.name: I pray that you all reach Eden safely.

rows.label: tlk001201_06_msg0004
rows.name: Zeke. Do not slack in your duties.

rows.label: tlk001201_06_msg0005
rows.name:
Quit sayin' it over and
over! I get it already!

rows.label: tlk001201_06_msg0007
rows.name:
If only I were a little younger, I
would have wanted to go with you...

rows.label: tlk001201_06_msg0008
rows.name: Heh, what a rambunctious old king...
